        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Public Land Recreational Opportunities Improvement Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes procedures for the issuance of special recreation permits on specified public land units for use by individuals and groups to engage in recreational activities at federal facilities or on federal recreational lands and waters.</p>]]></text>
